item.title: Tunes from Turtle Island S06E01
item.description: Indie, Hip Hop, RnB, Blues, Rez Metal, Dance, Rock, and Neo-soul from the music makers of the Seneca, Dena’ina, Oneida, Ojibwe, Inuit, Metis, Apache, and Navajo Nations. Brought to you by Tunes From Turtle Island and Pantheon Podcasts. Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/turtleisland

item.title: Week 19 – Eric Dickerson and Bill Cowher
item.description: Eric Dickerson joins Jim and Bill to discuss how hard it is to break records, why his is important to him, and what it was like getting a recruiting call from Coach Barry Switzer back in the day. Then, Bill Cowher sits down with Jim and Bill to share why he never went back into coaching, his thoughts on Jerod Mayo getting fired, and why a shared vision is needed for a team to succeed. Feed: https://feeds.simplecast.com/VQImumnT
